Well I just figured out how to make this a friend's only journal, thanks to Dannie, yes I know I am a loser. *_* So if you would like to be a friend comment here and I will add you! ^_^

I was extremely tired and I went to sleep. When I got up most everyone had left. Dannie is gone. Tony is at Dinner. Katie is reading HBP. And I am left here with Akito who is on idle. Haha. I think I will go read or something...Okay nvm, Tony just came back. Haha. Whew. I am not alone!!!!

On other news. I enjoyed the Half-Blood Prince very much but that just makes me want the seventh book even more. Haha. There is something buggin me about the way Dumbledore left and about Snape as well. Grrr, but I have two years to contemplate on it! X_X
